Senestech Company Profile 
SenesTech, Inc is a United States-based biotechnology platform and research company.
The Company is engaged in developing a technology for managing animal populations by fertility control.
It offers ContraPest, a fertility control product candidate.
ContraPest's technology and approach targets the reproductive capabilities of both sexes.
